        <h1>Wildcard</h1>

        <p>Wildcard is a browser extension that empowers anyone to modify websites to meet their own specific needs, using a familiar spreadsheet view. It's a research project as part of my PhD at MIT, with my advisor Daniel Jackson.</p>

